name: Summer
description: It was a summer night, when she came over to my table, and asked to watch me drawing with a shy smile. She ordered a cappuccino like she always did, and she knew how i like my black coffee sweet. Then rain poured down like they know the right moment to fall, makes our time there a lil bit longer than usual. It was a warm summer. When she was still there, across the table, watching me drawing.
